casebody.data: ALASKA, petitioner, Sally JEWELL, Secretary of the Interior, et al. No. 13-562. Supreme Court of the United States March 31, 2014. Case below, 720 F.3d 1214 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied. The CHIEF JUSTICE took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
